From {{der|en|frm|malléable}}, borrowed from {{der|en|LL.|malleābilis}}, derived from {{der|en|la|malleāre||to hammer}}, from {{m|la|malleus||hammer}}, from {{der|en|ine-pro|*mal-ni-||crushing}}, an extended variant of {{m|ine-pro|*melh₂-||crush, grind}}.

